6
00:01:01,436 --> 00:01:03,355
Dobro jutro, gospodine Talberg.
-Dobro jutro.

7
00:01:03,390 --> 00:01:05,816
Dobro jutro, Irving.
Zdravo.

8
00:01:05,851 --> 00:01:07,230
